<br>
I'd love to do it all again <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I took a small venture out two weeks ago to AZ with plans to see the meteor crater and the Grand Canyon, but due to finaces cut short (aka I loaned my younger sister 3/4 of my travel money for a small emergency) and my car overheating in Yuma, I wasn't able to go see and do everything that I'd planned.  But I had a blast!  Just being in the car, driving through the mountains at 3am and being able to see every star in the sky, knowing that I was miles away from the daily grind... all put me back in touch with myself, if even for a brief few hours.<br>
<br>
Oh well, so my Grand Canyon adventure waits another couple months <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   I'll see it within the next 6 months for sure, I've already promised myself that.<br>
